---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: <p>The Groove Library exists to explore rhythm as a global language.</p>

<p>Born from a decade of Afro-centric digging under the name Easton Chop Up, The Groove Library expands the lens — reaching across borders, eras and genres to document music built for movement, meaning and connection.</p>

<p>Through DJ mixes, live streams, guest selectors, album deep-dives and communal listening parties, The Groove Library curates sound as both archive and experience. It is a space for dancers, listeners, collectors and the curious — equally at home in ritual, roots, club systems and future experiments.</p>
<ul>
<li>There is no algorithm here.</li>
<li>No fixed genre.</li>
<li>No single destination.</li>
</ul>

Only the groove — shared, studied, celebrated and passed forward.
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="region region--lg bg-brand" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center">
      <div class="hero-logo">
        <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="" class="hero-logo__image" aria-hidden="true">
      </div>

      <div class="flow flow--md">
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl text-inverse">
          Welcome to The Groove Library
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-inverse mx-auto">
          A vibrant celebration of global music, featuring legendary mixes from around the world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cluster cluster--md justify-center">
        <fa-icon icon="globe" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
        <fa-icon icon="music" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
        <fa-icon icon="headphones" size="2x" class="text-inverse" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Mix Collection Section #}
<section class="region region--xl" aria-labelledby="mixes-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flow flow--xl">
      {# Section Header #}
      <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
        <h2 id="mixes-heading" class="text-3xl">
          Featured Mixes
        </h2>

        {% if theGrooveLibrary.count > 0 %}
          <div class="cluster cluster--sm justify-center">
            <span class="badge">
              <fa-icon icon="record-vinyl" size="sm" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
              {{ theGrooveLibrary.count }} mixes in this playlist
            </span>
            {% if theGrooveLibrary.fetchedAt %}
              <span class="badge badge--neutral">
                <fa-icon icon="clock" size="sm" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
                Updated {{ helpers.formatDate(theGrooveLibrary.fetchedAt) }}
              </span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      {# Mix Grid #}
      {% if helpers.hasItems(theGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts) %}
        <div class="grid grid--2" role="list" aria-label="Music mixes">
          {% for mix in theGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts %}
            <div role="listitem">
              {% include "mix-player.njk" %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% elif theGrooveLibrary.error %}
        {# Error State #}
        <div class="error" role="alert">
          <h3 class="error__title">
            <fa-icon icon="triangle-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
            Unable to load mixes
          </h3>
          <p>We encountered an error while fetching the music collection. Please try again later.</p>
          <details class="my-md">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-semibold">Technical details</summary>
            <p class="text-sm my-sm"><code>{{ theGrooveLibrary.error }}</code></p>
          </details>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        {# Empty State #}
        <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center py-3xl">
          <fa-icon icon="music-slash" size="4x" class="text-tertiary" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
          <div class="flow flow--sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl">No mixes available</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary">Check back soon for new content!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# About Section #}
<section class="region region--lg bg-secondary" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow">
      <div class="flow flow--lg text-center">
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-2xl">
          Music Without Borders
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          The Groove Library brings you carefully curated musical journeys from diverse cultures and traditions.
          Each mix is a story, a rhythm, a celebration of the universal language of music.
        </p>
        <div class="cluster cluster--lg justify-center">
          <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
            <fa-icon icon="earth-americas" size="3x" class="text-brand" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
            <p class="text-semibold">Global Sounds</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
            <fa-icon icon="heart" size="3x" class="text-brand" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
            <p class="text-semibold">Curated with Care</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
            <fa-icon icon="users" size="3x" class="text-brand" aria-hidden="true"></fa-icon>
            <p class="text-semibold">For Everyone</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
